      "id": "2005439529897910433",
      "text": "Another interesting moment during this meeting that many people didn’t pay much attention to: Vice President JD Vance was not present at the high-level meeting in Mar-a-Lago. \n\nAnd when Trump was asked about the negotiations team, he praised almost everyone - even Marco Rubio and Pete Hegseth (who were not very much involved) - but never mentioned JD Vance, who had been a very active participant in this process at the very beginning.\n\nI’m not a fan of conspiracy theories, so it would be good to simply ask JD Vance at the next opportunity where he was during this meeting.",
